name: ARAppClipCodeAnchor.URLDecodingState
desc: The states in the process of decoding an App Clip code URL.

items.name: case decoded
items.desc: A state that indicates the completed decoding of an App Clip Code URL.

items.name: case decoding
items.desc: A state that indicates the continuing process of decoding an App Clip Code's URL.

items.name: case failed
items.desc: A state that indicates the failure to decode an App Clip Code's URL.
